citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:05p on
24-Jul-19.
The inspector spoke with the licensee by text message. They stated they and their authorized persons were not
available for an inspection.
